songs.title: Yellow Alert
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1: Awkwafina]
10-10 WINS in the whip
Know I got the G.I. Joe kung fu grip
Been smoking on some government shit
This time last year on some 70's shit, ayy
Flow make a drunk girl strip
Others get mad when the yellow girl spit
Yellow girls cringe at a loud mouth bitch
Got Blues Clues peeps tryna muzzle my shit
Rep Queens on a motherland tip
On the boulevard, whole squad get lit
And the fuckboy squad from the car get flipped
You’s a thot in junior high, now you living off tips

[Hook: Awkwafina]
Get 'em all on yellow alert
Yellow alert make your grandma squirt
Get 'em all on yellow alert
Yellow alert make your grandma squirt

[Verse 2: Dumbfoundead]
Yellow girls, yellow boys so Springfield
Yellow pills got me struggling to sit still
Yellow veggies in my Yoshinoya chicken bowl
Got a motherfucker pissing gold, let's go
Trip you on your hoverboard and choke you doing smoke tricks
Smelling like papayas and your mama's playing dubstep
I can only take so much before this yellow boy flip
How you never lucky with a tattoo of a koi fish?

Yellow alert (skerrrt) you gon' get this work
Yellow alert (skerrrt) who an introvert?
Yellow alert (skerrrt) I'm mad
Use a better picture of me in your Asian studies class
God damn

[Hook: Awkwafina]
Get 'em all on yellow alert
Yellow alert make your grandma squirt
Get 'em all on yellow alert
Yellow alert make your grandma squirt

Kill 'em all like Robert Durst
Bitch, I kill 'em all like Robert Durst
Get 'em all on yellow alert
Yellow alert make your grandma squirt
